{"tid":2237772,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"下民易虐 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-10-10T14:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T14:14:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"effc633a94ab9e09b0c8708e8308383662af3a75","tid":2237772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201010/KLZHLAECANFSZMEIQRDHUMRNPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201010%2FKLZHLAECANFSZMEIQRDHUMRNPM%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=acbadbf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201010%2FKLZHLAECANFSZMEIQRDHUMRNPM%2F&h=95fb9037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201010/KLZHLAECANFSZMEIQRDHUMRNPM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n下民易虐 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E7M5luZiNBarDDcy6iZQgqXj9b8=/640x336/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MZNMEID4L5AORMDBMTLB4IL33Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE7M5luZiNBarDDcy6iZQgqXj9b8%3D%2F640x336%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMZNMEID4L5AORMDBMTLB4IL33Y.jpg&h=328fdb23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年10月1日被警察用真槍實彈擊中胸部的未成年少年曾志健，...........................<br />\n<br />\n案發時健仔手持兩呎長塑膠軟管拍打警察手臂，以常人邏輯，至多是襲警罪。與真槍實彈、全副裝備的防暴警相比，武力絕不對等，不對警察構成即時危險。警察在半公尺距離槍擊健仔胸口，子彈碎片擊中健仔肺部，距離心臟僅3cm，換言之，這個未成年少年與死神只有3cm之遙，能活下來，純粹是好運，而非警察手下留情。<br />\n<br />\n事發現場有媒體拍攝到警察疑曾經調包健仔的襲警工具，棄健仔的膠管不執，執起遠處長度達1米且尖頭的金屬長鐵枝。不過在今日香港，還有多少人敢寄望法庭會有公平、公正的審判？別說健仔只是一個手持軟膠管的未成年孩子，即使他是手持殺傷力武器的江洋大盜，警察在當時該不該開槍、開槍時射擊位置對不對、開槍後有沒有向嫌犯施救&hellip;&hellip;都須進行調查，調查結果也應向公眾交代。當然，警方甚麼也沒做，只是把健仔送上了法庭。<br />\n<br />\n同時被送上法庭的，還有理大博士生邱宏達，..........................<br />\n<br />\n香港的教育制度，曾經培養出這麼多情理兼備，有理想、有信念、不怕犧牲，但又充滿人性熱忱的人，這樣優秀的年輕人被一個一個送進冤獄，讓人垂淚。想起毓民新書，真是下民易虐，上天難欺。"},{"pid":"4e9da55e06baf0708b9bf416a2ed65119e242ed1","tid":2237772,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}